# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# NPRO Stats Backend - Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in the values
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Core Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PORT=8787
NODE_ENV=development
LOG_LEVEL=info

# Database (Railway Postgres or local)
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:password@localhost:5432/npro_stats?schema=public

# Secret for admin sync endpoints (generate a strong random string)
SYNC_SECRET=change-me-to-a-secure-secret

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NEAR RPC Configuration
# Comma-separated list of RPC endpoints for failover
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEAR_RPC_URLS=https://near.lava.build,https://rpc.mainnet.near.org,https://near.blockpi.network/v1/rpc/public,https://rpc.shitzuapes.xyz

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NearBlocks API Configuration (STRICT RATE LIMITING)
# Free tier: 6 calls/minute, 333 calls/day, 10,000 calls/month
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEARBLOCKS_BASE=https://api.nearblocks.io

# Comma-separated list of API keys for rotation
NEARBLOCKS_API_KEYS=your-nearblocks-api-key-1,your-nearblocks-api-key-2

# Header name for the API key (typically 'Authorization' or 'x-api-key')
NEARBLOCKS_API_HEADER=Authorization

# Prefix to put before the key value (e.g., 'Bearer ' - include trailing space if needed)
NEARBLOCKS_API_PREFIX=Bearer 

# Polling interval between NearBlocks requests (ms) - 15s = 4 calls/min
POLL_INTERVAL_MS=15000

# Page limit for paginated requests
PAGE_LIMIT=100

# How long to cool down a key after 429 (ms) - 3 minutes
NEARBLOCKS_KEY_COOLDOWN_MS=180000

# Request timeout (ms)
NEARBLOCKS_TIMEOUT_MS=10000

# Max retries for 5xx/timeout errors
NEARBLOCKS_MAX_RETRIES=3

# Max pages to fetch per sync run (protect daily quota)
NEARBLOCKS_MAX_PAGES_PER_RUN=20

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DexScreener API Configuration
# Rate limit: 300 requests/minute
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
DEXSCREENER_BASE=https://api.dexscreener.com
